  Bitcrush / Quantization
  - Radiohead — "Everything In Its Right Place" (bit-reduced vocal samples)                               
  - Aphex Twin — "Windowlicker" (deliberate sample rate and bit depth reduction throughout)               
  - Bon Iver — "715 - CR∑∑KS" (vocoder + low-resolution processing gives that grainy, staircase texture)
  - J Dilla — "Workinonit" (SP-303 sampler, which has 12-bit converters — built-in bitcrush)              
  - Early Akai MPC and E-mu SP-1200 hip-hop: the SP-1200's 12-bit converters are the defining sound of    
  golden-age boom bap  
